        heading: 'Building Your Evening Affirmation Ritual',
        content: 'Create a bedtime ritual that signals to your brain that the day is over. Turn off screens 30 minutes before bed, dim the lights, and open the Selfpause app. Listen to your recorded evening affirmations layered over ambient sounds like rain, ocean waves, or soft music. Set the app to fade out gradually so it does not disrupt your sleep onset. Many users find that within a week of consistent evening affirmation practice, their sleep quality improves noticeably. Your subconscious mind works overnight, so feeding it positive content before sleep is one of the highest-leverage practices you can adopt.',
